1081809864479797249.Text: Zak Penn publicly blasted Shane Black for a) ruining his script, and b) being an asshole, but in my estimation everything good in Last Action Hero came from Black's rewrite.

1081809220993871873.Title: Last Action Hero
1081809220993871873.Text: I'd go so far as to say this original draft of Last Action Hero is not good. The base conceit of being able to travel between movie and real world, and the meta commentary that comes with it is largely absent from the original script, which makes me wonder why it even sold.

1081799666776399872.Title: Last Action Hero
1081799666776399872.Text: It's also very clear that the original script for Last Action Hero was always intended to be an R rated movie. It wants to live in the LA of Lethal Weapon, not the cartoon funhouse that the film became.
